videos.description: Joe Harris drains the corner 3-pointer as Brad Stevens calls timeout to regroup his team in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harris' corner 3 forces timeout from Brad Stevens) 2021/5/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harris' corner 3 forces timeout from Brad Stevens

videos.description: Kyrie Irving is showered with boos from Celtics fans in his first game back in Boston with fans present.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Kyrie booed in return to Boston) 2021/5/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kyrie booed in return to Boston

videos.description: Jayson Tatum and Marcus Smart have the Boston crowd fired up as they hit 3-pointers to give the Celtics the lead at the end of the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum, Smart ignite Celtics to lead with 3-ball) 2021/5/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum, Smart ignite Celtics to lead with 3-ball

videos.description: Grant Williams swats James Harden's shot away at the rim late in the second quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Grant Williams shuts down Harden at the rim) 2021/5/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Grant Williams shuts down Harden at the rim

videos.description: Tristan Thompson throws down the monstrous dunk to get Celtics fans excited in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Thompson throws down two-handed jam to start 3rd quarter) 2021/5/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson throws down two-handed jam to start 3rd quarter

videos.description: Jayson Tatum nonchalantly lands the and-1 shot on Kyrie Irving as the Celtics extend their lead to 13 in the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum's and-1 on Kyrie extends Celts' lead) 2021/5/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum's and-1 on Kyrie extends Celts' lead

videos.description: Tristan Thompson takes off for the massive putback jam as the Celtics are cruising in Game 3.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Thompson throws down putback jam over Nets) 2021/5/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Thompson throws down putback jam over Nets

videos.description: Jayson Tatum drains the contested jumper over Kevin Durant as the Celtics are up late on the Nets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum reaches 50 with tough shot over KD) 2021/5/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum reaches 50 with tough shot over KD

videos.description: As Jayson Tatum gives his postgame interview, his son Deuce runs wild on the Celtics' court after the win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Deuce runs wild on court as dad Jayson gives interview) 2021/5/28 ESHEET

videos.headline: Deuce runs wild on court as dad Jayson gives interview

videos.description: Jayson Tatum puts up a staggering 50 points as the Celtics return to Boston and take Game 3 from the Nets.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Tatum sets playoff career high with 50 as Celtics steal Game 3 from Nets) 2021/5/28 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Tatum sets playoff career high with 50 as Celtics steal Game 3 from Nets
